(WIP)
Role: Neutral anomaly
Concept: Broken memory ghosts
Visual: Semi-humanoid translucent distortions with fractured edges. Slight polygonal glitches in silhouette.
Behavior: Replay fragments of erased individuals. Rarely aware. Rarely tangible.

Artist Direction: Glitchy transparency, edges splitting into geometric fragments.

Design Strength: These are emotional anchors. Don’t overcomplicate them.